<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>E-Commerce</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/product-styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav></nav>
    <main>
      <section id="product">
        <img
          src="<%= product.imageUrl %>"
          alt="product image"
          id="product-image"
        />
        <div id="product-info">
          <h3 class="product-name"><%= product.productName %></h3>
          <p class="product-price">$ <%= product.price %> USD</p>
          <div class="info-details">
            <div class="headings">
              <span id="Info" class="darkBorderBottom">Info</span>
              <span id="Details">Details</span>
              <span id="Shipping">Shipping</span>
            </div>
            <div class="paragraphs">
              <span id="Info-Para" class="visibleTransition"
                >Get ready to elevate your denim game with our stylish and
                versatile high waisted jeans. These jeans are designed to
                flatter your figure and provide a comfortable fit that
                accentuates your curves. The high-rise waistline not only
                elongates your legs but also offers a sleek and slimming
                effect.</span
              >
              <span id="Details-Para"
                >The high-rise waistline not only elongates your legs but also
                offers a sleek and slimming effect. Crafted from premium quality
                denim, these jeans are durable and built to withstand everyday
                wear. These high waisted jeans are a must-have in every
                fashion-savvy wardrobe.</span
              >
              <span id="Shipping-Para"
                >The estimated delivery time will vary based on your location
                and the shipping method selected. We strive to process and
                dispatch orders promptly, typically within 1-2 business days.
                Please note that delivery times may be longer during peak
                seasons or due to unforeseen circumstances.</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="options">
            <div id="available-colors">
              <p>Color</p>
              <div id="color-list"></div>
            </div>
            <div id="available-sizes">
              <p>Size</p>
              <div id="size-list"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="checkout-section">
            <div class="quantity">
              <p>Quantity</p>
              <input type="number" name="" id="quantity" min="1" value="1" />
            </div>
            <% if (inCart == true) { %>
                <button id="remove-from-cart">remove from Cart</button>
                <button id="add-to-cart" style="display: none;">Add to Cart</button>
            <% } else { %>
                <button id="add-to-cart">Add to Cart</button>
                <button id="remove-from-cart" style="display: none;">remove from Cart</button>
            <% } %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <script>
      var productInfo = JSON.parse('<%- JSON.stringify(product) -%>')
    </script>
    <script src="/product.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
